# Authors & Contributors

This file lists the people who have contributed to Nowa Desktop.

## Main Authors

* Alexandre Magro - Initial work and maintainer

## Contributors

Thank you to everyone who has contributed to this project!

## Acknowledgments

This project was inspired by and incorporates ideas from:

* **ElementaryOS WingPanel** - Adaptive panel behavior based on wallpaper analysis
* **GNOME Rounded Corners** (by lennart-k) - Rounded screen corners implementation
  - Repository: https://github.com/lennart-k/gnome-rounded-corners
* **Night Theme Switcher** (by rmnvgr) - Automatic theme switching logic
  - Repository: https://gitlab.com/rmnvgr/nightthemeswitcher-gnome-shell-extension

Special thanks to all the GNOME Shell extension developers who share their code and knowledge with the community.
